      req[&quot;parameter6&quot;] = &quot;value6&quot;
    }

pass this `req` object as a request body in API call

Just for note (additional tip):

retrofit either keeps all null parameterized value or remove null parameter value, directly from the object, depending upon configuritation we set for `Convertor.Factory` value while building retrofit service object. This you can use in certain scenarios where null values not required or required.

   

     //to keep null value params in object
        val convertorFactory= GsonConverterFactory.create(GsonBuilder().serializeNulls().create())    
    
    //or
    
        // eliminate null params
        val convertorFactory= GsonConverterFactory.create()
    
        return Retrofit.Builder().addConverterFactory(convertorFactory)

